Version 1.11.1
- finished updating market price impact calculations
- now takes into account the new different costs for expanding RGOs
- adds cost breakdown for RGOs that matches the breakdown available for buildings
- fixes check for available workers to account for the addition of estate-specific population growth
- shows the available workers and the expected monthly change in workers the the RGO and auto-expand tooltips
- updates the min/max discount limits for auto-building so you can now set the max penalty cost up to 150% to match the new max penalty cost from patch 1.2
- corrects the color of the discount change value in the tooltips for setting minimum discount
